-->

    <p>This is another paragraph.</p>

    <h4>3.3 HTML Link</h4>
    <p><a href="https://www.w3schools.com" target="_blank">This is a link to W3Schools</a></p>

    <h4>3.4 HTML Image</h4>
    <p><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3f/Logo_PENS.png" alt="Logo PENS" width="100"><br>
    Politeknik Elektronika Negeri Surabaya</p>

    <h4>3.5 Garis Horizontal</h4>
    <p>Tag &lt;hr&gt; mendefinisikan garis horizontal:</p>
    <hr>
    <p>This is a paragraph.</p>

    <h4>3.6 Ganti Baris</h4>
    <p>This is<br>a para<br>graph with line breaks</p>

    <h4>3.7 Format Teks HTML</h4>
    <p><b>This text is bold</b></p>
    <p><i>This text is italic</i></p>
    <p><u>This text is underlined</u></p>
    <p>This is <sub>subscript</sub> and <sup>superscript</sup></p>

    <h4>3.8 HTML Table</h4>
    <table>
        <tr><th>Firstname</th><th>Lastname</th><th>Points</th></tr>
        <tr><td>Jill</td><td>Smith</td><td>50</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Eve</td><td>Jackson</td><td>94</td></tr>
        <tr><td>John</td><td>Doe</td><td>80</td></tr>
    </table>

    <h4>3.9 HTML List</h4>
    <p><b>Unordered List</b></p>
    <ul>
        <li>Apples</li>
        <li>Bananas</li>
        <li>Lemons</li>
        <li>Oranges</li>
    </ul>

    <p><b>Ordered List</b></p>
    <ol>
        <li>HTML</li>
        <li>CSS</li>
        <li>JavaScript</li>
    </ol>

    <h4>3.10 HTML Layout</h4>
    <div class="layout">
        <div class="layout-header">Main Title of Web Page</div>
